1 TITL Gaspare Natale
1 NOTE @N00011@
1 SOUR @S00027@
0 @N00011@ NOTE geni:about_me On an entry in the Baptism of SPITERI Ignazia daughter of Angelo
1 CONT and Caterina dite Caterinella on 1622-11-10 at La Matrice, there was a note
1 CONT stipulating
1 CONT
1 CONT   * "said son of Gaspare and Agata (he remarries in 1625 with Angelica born SPITERI daughter of Antonio)" However, the entry is of a girl, Moreover there is a marriage on 1625-02-10 at Kirkop Parish between:
1 CONT
1 CONT   * SPITERI Gasparo
1 CONT
1 CONT   * and Angelica Husband is from Gozo, and wife is widow of Antonio MIRRIOL
1 CONT
1 CONT But, there is also a marriage on 1625-03-10 at St Georges-Rabat between:
1 CONT
1 CONT   * SPITERI Angelo son of Gasparo
1 CONT
1 CONT   * and SPITERI Angelica daughter of Gasparo _Could be a mistake because of the missing info and similar dates to marriage mentioned above_
1 CONT
1 CONT \----
1 CONT
1 CONT Parents of Gaspare are missing both from the marriage index and the burial
1 CONT records. Moreover, there is a confusion with regards to Gaspare Natale since
1 CONT there's two entries under:
1 CONT
1 CONT   * Gaspare buried on 30 July 1642
1 CONT
1 CONT   * Natale buried on 27 November 1601
1 CONT
1 CONT \----
1 CONT
1 CONT Also, there is a marriage at Haz Zebbug on 1589-10-13 between Barbara Vincenzo
1 CONT and Spiteri Gioanella, were a note reads that Gaspare the wife's brother was a
1 CONT witness at the wedding. There is a possibly.
