0 @N00267@ NOTE geni:about_me
1 CONT **Federico** , nato non prima del 1259 e morto il 22 luglio 1305,
1 CONT
1 CONT   * ebbe un figlio di nome Corrado, nato verso il 1280 e morto dopo il 1320;
1 CONT
1 CONT
1 CONT # <https://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/federico-d-antiochia_(Dizionario-
1 CONT Biografico)/>
1 CONT \---------
1 CONT
1 CONT -<http://fmg.ac/Projects/MedLands/GERMANY,%20Kings.htm#CorradoAntiochiadied1301>
1 CONT
1 CONT i) FEDERIGO (-Palermo 22 Jul 1305). The Historia Sicula of Bartolomeo di
1 CONT Neocastro names "Fridericus, Henricus et Galvanus" as the children of
1 CONT "Conradus de Antiochia" and his wife[753]. An epigraph records the death 22
1 CONT Jul 1305 of "Dominus Fridericus miles…domini Conradi di Antiochia comitis
1 CONT filius et reverendi patris Bartholomæi Archiep. Parnorm. frater"[754].
1 CONT
1 CONT m ---. The name of Federigo´s wife is not known. Federigo & his wife had one
1 CONT child:
1 CONT
1 CONT
1 CONT   * (a) CORRADO (-after [1320]). The primary source which confirms his parentage has not yet been identified.
