1 CONT him he was a lover of verse, not prose. He favoured the troubadours, of which
1 CONT he himself was one, and wrote two sirventesos.
1 CONT
1 CONT The first is in the form of an exchange between Peter and one Peironet, a
1 CONT jongleur. The second forms part of a compilation of five compositions from
