1 CONT -<http://fmg.ac/Projects/MedLands/MONFERRATO,%20SALUZZO,%20SAVONA.htm#BeatriceLanciaMCorradoAntiochia>
1 CONT
1 CONT 5\. BEATRICE (-after 1268). The Historia Sicula of Bartolomeo di Neocastro
1 CONT records that "comes…Galvanus Beatricem filiam suam" married "Conradus de
1 CONT Antiochia"[869]. Her parentage and marriage are confirmed by the Istoria of
