1 CONT Cabrera had occupied the County of Urgell in opposition to Aurembiax, the
1 CONT heiress of Ermengol VIII, who had died without sons in 1208. While Aurembiax's
1 CONT mother, Elvira, had made herself a protegée of James's father, on her death
