1 CONT Like his grandfather, ascended to the crown at the age of five. It was run by
1 CONT a regency until he came of age; and his uncle Sanc, Count of Provence,
1 CONT managed the finances and paid off his father's debts. He later became known
1 CONT for leading military campaigns that captured Majorca and the other Balearic
1 CONT islands, as well as Valencia, from the Moors.
