1 CONT He was placed under regency at 5 years old of his great-uncle Count Sancho of
1 CONT Roussillin (in Aragon, now in France) until 1218 and began to govern on his
1 CONT own in 1227. He extended his kingdom by conquest and by marrying a daughter
1 CONT of Alfonso VIII of Castile. By his 2nd wife, he had many children, but made
