1 CONT a) MARGHERITA di Poli (-after 1246/49]). The Historia Sicula of Bartolomeo di
1 CONT Neocastro records that "Fridericus" married "Margharitam filiam N. de Romanis
1 CONT cunabulis editam"[19]. The primary source which confirms her parentage more
1 CONT precisely has not yet been identified.
1 CONT
1 CONT **m** FEDERIGO di Antiochia, illegitimate son of Emperor FRIEDRICH II & his
1 CONT mistress Maria [Matilda] --- ([1221]-killed in battle Foggia 1256).
1 CONT
1 CONT \---------
1 CONT
1 CONT **Margherita** era figlia del nobile romano Giovanni Conti signore di Poli
1 CONT (era figlio di Riccardo, fratello di Innocenzo III)
1 CONT
