1 CONT 1\. MANFREDO [II] (-[1214/15]). Marchese di Busca. .. ...
1 CONT
1 CONT m **BIANCA Maletta** , daughter of GUGLIELMO Maletta & his wife --- (-after
1 CONT [1214/15]). Her marriage is confirmed by the Thomas Tusci Gesta Imperatorum et
1 CONT Pontificum which refers to the mother of "Manfredus" as "sorore marchionis
1 CONT Lancee…filia domne Blanca"[797]. Her parentage is suggested by the charters in
1 CONT which Manfredo King of Sicily refers to two members of the Maletta family as
1 CONT "avunculus" (see below).
1 CONT Manfredo [II] & his wife had eight children:
