1 CONT [On his succession to the crown, Louis commanded King Henry III,ofEngland to
1 CONT attend his coronation, as a vassal, but instead, Henry sent todemand
1 CONT restitution of allt he provinces taken from his father byPhilippe-Auguste
1 CONT (KingPhilippe II). This was sufficient to rekindlehostilities. Prompted by
