1 CONT good Count Raymond of Provence.", Villani's Chronicle, Being Selections from
1 CONT the First Nine Books of the Croniche Fiorentine of Giovanni Villani (London:
1 CONT Archibald Constable & Co.), 196. The Provençal coblas and cansos referred to
1 CONT do not survive and Ramon Berenguer is not listed among the troubadours, though
1 CONT he was their patron.
