1 CONT later annulled. Married in Valladolid between 1/16 December 1197 with King
1 CONT Alfonso IX of León as her second wife. After their marriage was dissolved on
1 CONT grounds of consanguinity in 1204, she returned to her homeland and became
1 CONT regent of her minor brother King Henry I. Queen of Castile in her own right
1 CONT after the death of Henry I in 1214, immediately abdicated in favor of her son.
