1 CONT Married in Burgos before 29 August 1215 with Infanta Mafalda of Portugal, the
1 CONT union was unconsummated and dissolved in 1216 on grounds of consanguinity.
1 CONT Soon after his divorce was betrothed with Infanta Sancha of León, eldest
1 CONT daughter of King Alfonso IX and stepdaughter of her oldest sister, but died
1 CONT killed by a tile coming off a roof before the marriage could be solemnized.
1 CONT
1 CONT [edit] Notes
1 CONT
