1 CONT MEDI ManuscriptAlfonso VIII, King of Castile, victor at the battle of LasNavas
1 CONT de
1 CONT Tolosa, which forever tipped the Iberian scales in favor of the
1 CONT christians. He married Eleanor, daughter of Henry II of England, and
1 CONT Eleanor of Aquitaine. In addition to son Enrique I (who d.s.p.) he had
1 CONT several daughters, including the wife of Louis VIII.
