1 CONT Eleanor was baptized by Cardinal Henry of Pisa. Her godfather was Rob ert of
1 CONT Torigni. At the time of her sister Joan's death 24 September 1 199, Eleanor
1 CONT was in Castile. It is reported that she maintained a ver y gracious court for
1 CONT her husband Alfonso.
