0 @N00682@ NOTE geni:about_me * <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_of_Geneva> _(ITA
1 CONT better)_
1 CONT
1 CONT She was supposed to become the third wife of Philip II of France but was
1 CONT abducted by Thomas I of Savoy in 1195, while on her way to Paris. Thomas then
1 CONT married her himself, claiming that Philip II was already married (the French
1 CONT King had married Ingeborg of Denmark in 1193 but had repudiated her soon
1 CONT thereafter)
1 CONT
1 CONT
1 CONT ==The children of Marguerite and Thomas I of Savoy were:==
1 CONT
1 CONT
1 CONT   * Amadeus IV of Savoy (1197 - 1253)
1 CONT
1 CONT   * Umberto (d.1223)
1 CONT
