1 CONT invasion of 1241 and fled to Dalmatia. Approximately half the population was
1 CONT killed by the invading armies. He was eventually able to reestablish himself
1 CONT and defeated the Tartar Nogai Khan in 12?1. He had two sons and seven
1 CONT daughters, the most famous being St. Margaret of Hungary.
