1 CONT
1 CONT In the Image: The coronation of John of Brienne as King of Jerusalem, with
1 CONT Maria of Montferrat, from a late 13th century MS of the Histoire d'Outremer,
1 CONT painted in Acre. (Biblioteca Medicea-Laurenziana, Florence).
