1 CONT He was a French nobleman who ruled as King of Jerusalem from 1210 to 1225.
1 CONT Jean De Brienne
1 CONT [http://trees.ancestry.com/rd?f=image&guid=01c187fc-2ed7-4fb7-8043-ca7ed7addcdc&tid=9692367&pid=-524891591](http://trees.ancestry.com/rd?f=image&guid=01c187fc-2ed7-4fb7-8043-ca7ed7addcdc&tid=9692367&pid=-524891591)
