0 @N00750@ NOTE geni:about_me * <https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guillaume_Ier_de_Gen%C3%A8ve>
1 CONT
1 CONT -<http://fmg.ac/Projects/MedLands/burgkgenev.htm#GuillaumeIGenevadied1196B>
1 CONT
1 CONT GUILLAUME [I] de Genève, son of AMEDEE [I] Comte de Genève & his first wife
1 CONT Mathilde de Cuiseaux ([1131/37]-25 Jul 1196). "Amedeus Gebennensis comes"
1 CONT donated property to the monastery of Abondance "in manu…consanguinei mei
1 CONT domini Bocardis ipsius ecclesiæ abbatis", for the souls of "patris mei Aymonis
1 CONT et matris meæ Itæ et Willelmi fratris mei et Matildis uxoris mæ" and for the
1 CONT protection of "filiorum meorum Wilelmi et Amedei", by charter dated 1153[70].
1 CONT "Amedeus Gebennensium comes…et filius eius Guillelmus" restored the rights of
1 CONT the bishopric of Geneva, with the consent of "Amedeus quoque junior filius
1 CONT comitis", by undated charter[71]. Comte de Genève. "Willelmus…Gebennensis
1 CONT comes" founded the Chartreuse monstery of Pommiers, with the consent of
1 CONT "Humbertus filius meus…B. quoque uxor mea et filius meus Aymo quinquennis", by
1 CONT charter dated 1179[72]. A charter dated 1187 records an arbitration concerning
1 CONT the differences between "Wilielmum comitem Gebenn." and the bishop of
1 CONT Geneva[73]. "Wilermus Gebennensium et Valdensium comes" confirmed donations by
1 CONT "bonæ memorie predecessoris mei Aymonis [error for Amedei] comitis", with the
1 CONT consent of "Humbertus filius meus", by charter dated 1192, witnessed by
1 CONT "Turumbertus de Lucingio"[74].
1 CONT
1 CONT **m** firstly AGNES de Savoie, daughter of AMEDEE III Comte de Savoie & his
1 CONT second wife Mathilde d'Albon ([1136/45?]-before 1172). The death is recorded
1 CONT "Pridie Kal Aug" in 1194 of "dna Juliana abb.sa Sc.ti Andreæ", noting
1 CONT donations by "f.ris sui Humberti comiti Sabaudiæ" and "Agnetis sororis sue
1 CONT Gebennensis comitisse"[75].
1 CONT
1 CONT **m** secondly BEATRIX de Faucigny, daughter of AIMON [I] Seigneur de Faucigny
1 CONT & his wife ---. "Willelmus…Gebennensis comes" founded the Chartreuse monstery
1 CONT of Pommiers, with the consent of "Humbertus filius meus…B. quoque uxor mea et
1 CONT filius meus Aymo quinquennis", by charter dated 1179[76]. Her parentage is
1 CONT confirmed by the Chronicle of Alberic de Trois-Fontaines which names her
1 CONT daughter "Margareta filia domni de Fusceneis de matre Guilelmi, filii Humberti
1 CONT comitis Gebenensis" as wife of "comitis Thome de Sabaudia"[77].
1 CONT
1 CONT Guillaume [I] & his first wife had one child:
