1 CONT France.
1 CONT
1 CONT She also married Humbert III "Le Saint", Count of Savoy.
1 CONT
1 CONT Father: Gerard I, Count of Macon and Vienne, b. ca. 1132 in Vienne, Isere,
1 CONT France, d. 15 September 1184
1 CONT
