1 CONT Erard II, Comte de Brienne was the son of Walter II, Comte de Brienne and
1 CONT Humbleline (?).2 He married Agnes de Montfaucon, daughter of Richard II, Comte
1 CONT de Montbellard, in 1166.1 He died on 8 February 1191 at Acre, Israel.1
1 CONT
1 CONT Erard II, Comte de Brienne fought in the Third Crusade.1 He succeeded to the
1 CONT title of Comte de Brienne circa 1158.1 He fought in the siege of Acre on 8
1 CONT February 1191.1
