1 CONT <http://genealogy.euweb.cz/piast/piast4.html> The senior branch inherited
1 CONT Silesia, which they subdivided relentlessly until it comprised several small
1 CONT states. Within a couple generations the Silesians drifted away from their
1 CONT Polish loyalties and came under the Bohemian (and, more generally, the German)
1 CONT ambit.
