0 @N00881@ NOTE geni:about_me Frederick of Bohemia
1 CONT
1 CONT From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
1 CONT
1 CONT By his marriage to Elizabeth, daughter of Geza II of Hungary, he had the
1 CONT following issue:
1 CONT
1 CONT Helena (b.1158), affianced to Peter, son of Manuel I Comnenus, in 1164
1 CONT
1 CONT Sophia (died 25 May 1185), married Albert, Margrave of Meissen
1 CONT
1 CONT Ludmilla (died 14 August 1240), married Adalbert VI, count of Bogen, and then
1 CONT Louis I, Duke of Bavaria
1 CONT
1 CONT Vratislaus (d.1180)
1 CONT
1 CONT Olga (fl.c.1163)
1 CONT
