1 CONT of the Rhine from 1195 to 1212.
1 CONT
1 CONT Henry V, Count Palatine of the Rhine
1 CONT
1 CONT From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
1 CONT
1 CONT In 1193, Henry married Agnes (died 1204), daughter of Conrad, Count Palatine
1 CONT of the Rhine. Around 1209, he married Agnes (died 1248), daughter of Conrad
1 CONT II, Margrave of Lower Lusatia. He had the following children, all from the
1 CONT first marriage:
1 CONT
1 CONT Henry (1197–1214)
1 CONT
1 CONT Irmgard (died 1260), married Herman V, Margrave of Baden-Baden
1 CONT
1 CONT Agnes (died 1267), married Otto II Wittelsbach, Duke of Bavaria
