1 CONT
1 CONT **Constance Arpád** is the daughter of **Béla III Arpád, King of Hungary** and
1 CONT **Agnes de Châtillon**. (2) She married **Premysl Ottokar I, King of Bohemia**
1 CONT , son of Vladislav I, King of Bohemia and Judith von Thuringe, in 1198. (3)
1 CONT
1 CONT
1 CONT   * She died in 1240. (3)
1 CONT
1 CONT   * Children of Constance Arpád and Premysl Ottokar I, King of Bohemia
1 CONT
1 CONT # Anne of Bohemia+ (3) b. 1204, d. 1265
1 CONT # Wenceslas I, King of Bohemia+ (3) b. 1205, d. 1253
1 CONT # Wladislaw, Margrave of Moravia (3) b. 1207, d. 1227
1 CONT # Premysl, Margrave of Moravia (3) b. 1209, d. 1239
1 CONT # Agnes 'the Saint' of Bohemia (3) b. 1211, d. 1282
1 CONT
